		<div id=\"lingua-list\"><h4>This post is also available in:</h4><dl>	<dt>Fran\x{e7}ais: </dt>		<dd><a href=\"http://fr.globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/10/11826/\">Cor\x{e9}e du Nord : Deux journalistes am\x{e9}ricaines condamn\x{e9}es aux travaux forc\x{e9}s...</a></dd>	<dt>bahasa Indonesia: </dt>		<dd><a href=\"http://id.globalvoicesonline.org/2009/06/1443/\">Korea Utara: Dua Jurnalis AS Dihukum Kerja Paksa...</a></dd></dl></div>			
